HEADWORD: Ignigenous
<hw>Ig*nig"e*nous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>ignigenus</ets>; <ets>ignis</ets> fire + <ets>genere</ets>,
<ets>ginere</ets>, to beget, produce.]</ety> <def>Produced by the action
of fire, as lava.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

